ude_opus_4_6\": 2.2164,\n      \"claude_sonnet_4_6\": 1.3299,\n      \"claude_haiku_4_5\": 0.4433,\n      \"gpt5_latest\": 4.4329\n    },\n    \"powered_by\": \"jcodemunch-mcp by jgravelle \\u00b7 https://github.com/jgravelle/jcodemunch-mcp\"\n  }\n}","title":"","metadata":{"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773351525382,"end":1773351525389},"attachments":[]}}}
